oads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-ingredients\"\u003eIngredients \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhiskey\u003c/strong\u003e – Jack Daniel’s Tennessee Whiskey is a great, classic choice.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTriple-Sec\u003c/strong\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLemon Juice\u003c/strong\u003e – Fresh squeezed.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLemon-Lime Soda\u003c/strong\u003e – Such as Sprite or 7Up.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/lynchburg-lemonade/?tp_image_id=136451\" data-pin-title=\"Lynchburg Lemonade Recipe\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade-.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--156x125.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%20960\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade--156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade-.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-instructions\"\u003eInstructions \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn a cocktail shaker, combine the Tennessee whiskey, triple sec and fresh lemon juice with ice. Shake for 10 to 15 seconds until it is ice cold. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003ePour into a highball glass with fresh ice and top off with lemon-lime soda. You may also serve this cocktail in a mason jar. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/lynchburg-lemonade/?tp_image_id=136452\" data-pin-title=\"Lynchburg Lemonade Recipe\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.-.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--156x125.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%20960\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.--156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade.-.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eGarnish with lemon slices or wedges and fresh mint leaves. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-tips-for-making\"\u003eTips for Making \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSome recipes call for \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/make-your-own-sour-mix/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003esour mix\u003c/a\u003e rather than lemon juice. We’ll let you choose your own adventure. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eGarnish ideas: Lemon slices or wedges and fresh mint make great garnishes for this drink.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eIf you want to make a big batch, 8x this recipe and make it ahead in a pitcher, excluding the lemon-lime soda, which should be added when serving.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/lynchburg-lemonade/?tp_image_id=136453\" data-pin-title=\"Lynchburg Lemonade Recipe\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lynchburg-Lemonade-1-1.jpg 1200w, http